      <title>BP 开始从 Greater Tortue 产气，预计很快可交付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/bp-starts-gas-output-from-greater-tortue-with-delivery-seen-soon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国石油公司的大托尔图艾哈迈因项目已开始从塞内加尔和毛里塔尼亚的海上油田生产天然气，两国都期待着很快实现天然气供应，以促进经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/bp-starts-gas-output-from-greater-tortue-with-delivery-seen-soon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 08:57:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯和乌克兰结束五十年的欧洲天然气输送</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/russia-and-ukraine-end-five-decades-of-gas-transit-to-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在基辅拒绝允许任何为莫斯科战争机器提供资金的过境后，俄罗斯停止通过乌克兰向欧洲输送天然气，关闭了一条运营了五十年的路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/russia-and-ukraine-end-five-decades-of-gas-transit-to-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 08:54:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
